extends layout/app

block page
   div(class="g-wrap")
      div(class="outer-bg")
         include chunk/header
         main(class="g-main")
            div(class="hero")
               div(class="hero__video")
                  video(autoplay="" loop="" muted="")
                     source(src="https://video.wixstatic.com/video/d0d56f_00c07f129fe64d818c96587e2b73e4f8/1080p/mp4/file.mp4" type="video/mp4") 
               div(class="hero__wrapper container")
                  h1(class="hero__title h1") Global Software Development
                  div(class="hero__subtitle") A leading provider of cutting-edge software, Invatechs assists customers in bringing ideas to life and elevating their products.
                  div(class="hero__btn main-btn")
                     a(href="") Let's work together
                  div(class="hero__cta main-cta")
                     a(href="") Check our cases
            div(class="main-services services dark-bg")
               div(class="services__wrapper container")
                  div(class="title-wrap")
                     div(class="services__title title") Our Services
                  div(class="services__cards cards")
                     div(class="cards__item")
                        div(class="card__title title-yellow") Web Development
                        div(class="card__text") Our effective solutions are aimed at creating user-friendly and functional platforms and websites.
                     div(class="cards__item")
                        div(class="card__title title-yellow") Mobile Development
                        div(class="card__text") As an app development company, we are ready to use modern technologies and patterns to create eye-catching and trending mobile applications.
                     div(class="cards__item")
                        div(class="card__title title-yellow") Bespoke Software
                        div(class="card__text") Our team works closely with clients to understand their requirements and provide customized software solutions to meet their unique requirements and goals.
                     div(class="cards__item")
                        div(class="card__title title-yellow") Software Testing
                        div(class="card__text") Our QA services will give an objective assessment of your product, allowing you to stay on trend in the fast-growing market in your niche.
            div(class="why-choose choose")
               div(class="choose__wrapper container")
                  div(class="choose__col choose__col-text")
                     div(class="choose__title h2") Why choose Invatechs?
                     div(class="choose__texts")
                        p Invatechs provides top-notch custom application development services, utilizing their knowledge and experience to create one-of-a-kind solutions that meet each customer's specific goals and requirements.
                        p We always find an individual approach to every idea of our customers, offering a wide range of IT services and knowledge that can help businesses succeed in today's market. Invatechs has qualified specialists from different areas who constantly improve their abilities to create trendsetting products. We always offer unique solutions that can be implemented in the most comfortable time frame.
                        p Our core competency is financial technologies, and however, after ten years of prosperity, we have excelled in other business areas. Invatechs has also completed many projects in Logistics, eCommerce, Real Estate, and Restaurants. Our products are continuously optimized and secured against cyber threats. We always seek a long-term partnership to benefit your business, saving time and budget.
                  div(class="choose__col choose__col-numbers numbers")
                     div(class="numbers__item")
                        div(class="numbers__item-num") 10+
                        div(class="numbers__item-text") years of expertise
                     div(class="numbers__item")
                        div(class="numbers__item-num") 93%
                        div(class="numbers__item-text") recurring customers
                     div(class="numbers__item")
                        div(class="numbers__item-num") 100+
                        div(class="numbers__item-text") successful projects
            div(class="experts-industries")
               div(class="experts-industries__title container h2") We are experts in such industries as
            include chunk/block-industries-slider
            include chunk/block-technologies-slider
            div(class="main-cases")
               div(class="cases__wrapper")
                  a(class="cases__btn")
                     span Go to all Case Studies
                     img(src="img/technologies__arrow_right.svg", alt="Go to all Case Studies")
                  div(class="cases__item item dark-bg bg-text")
                     div(class="item__wrapper container")
                        div(class="info-wrap")
                           div(class="item__info")
                              div(class="cases__title title") Case Studies
                              div(class="item__subtitle") Open Banking
                              div(class="item__text") InvaBank is a cutting-edge online banking application that is built using Invatechs’ white-label solution. This solution includes a variety of standard UI/UX elements and necessary functionality that allows the app to work seamlessly as an online banking service, supporting Open Banking API.
                              div(class="item__tags tags")
                                 a(class="tags__item") FinTech
                                 a(class="tags__item") Open-Banking
                                 a(class="tags__item") API
                              div(class="item__btn main-arr-btn")
                                 a(href="") Learn more
                           div(class="item__image")
                              div(class="image-wrap")
                                 img(src="img/case-studies__image-1.png", alt="Case srtudies")

                  div(class="cases__item dark-side-bg bg-text")
                     div(class="item__wrapper container")
                        div(class="info-wrap")
                           div(class="item__info")
                              div(class="item__subtitle") Vance Pay
                              div(class="item__text") Our customer's mission is to improve people's financial well-being by giving them access to unpaid wages on demand. They want to empower employees to meet short-term liabilities by providing them with access to their uncollected income in exchange for a fair transaction fee and access to effective personalized financial management tools.
                              div(class="item__tags tags")
                                 a(class="tags__item") FinTech
                                 a(class="tags__item") Wealth-Managment
                              div(class="item__btn main-arr-btn")
                                 a(href="") Learn more
                           div(class="item__image")
                              div(class="image-wrap")
                                 img(src="img/case-studies__image-2.png", alt="Case srtudies")

                  div(class="cases__item dark-bg bg-text")
                     div(class="item__wrapper container")
                        div(class="info-wrap")
                           div(class="item__info")
                              div(class="item__subtitle") Cryptocurrency Saving Application
                              div(class="item__text")
                                 p The app offers three ways to invest:
                                 ul
                                    li One-time investments: simply invest once any sums whenever you want
                                    li Recurring deposit: set up the amount of money you want to invest into cryptocurrency every week or month and it will be withdrawn automatically
                                    li Round ups: the app tracks user’s transactions and rounds up his daily purchases to the nearest $1, $2 or $5 and accumulates the difference to a certain amount of money and then automatically invest it into cryptocurrency
                              div(class="item__tags tags")
                                 a(class="tags__item") FinTech
                                 a(class="tags__item") Blockchain and Cryptocurrency
                              div(class="item__btn main-arr-btn")
                                 a(href="") Learn more
                           div(class="item__image")
                              div(class="image-wrap")
                                 img(src="img/case-studies__image-3.png", alt="Case srtudies")
            include chunk/block-customers-reviews
            include chunk/block-customers-slider

            include chunk/footer